"Procurement of matured De Marmoth meat":
"The meat of the De Mammoth is easy to
procure, and it is also a popular food. But I
have not procured the meat of the matured
De Marmoth before, and this is still an
unknown. Therefore, I have a request to you!
I would like you to bring me the meat of the
matured De Marmoth!

*Target De Marmoth of Lv.60 and above"
"老成したデ・マルモスの肉の調達"

"デ・マルモスのお肉って、調理しやすいし
結構人気の食材なんだけど、
老成したデ・マルモスの肉はまだ
取り扱った事ないし、未知数なのよね。
そこであなたにお願い！
老成したデ・マルモスのお肉を
持ってきて欲しいの！

※Lv.60～のデ・マルモスが対象"
